0the%20remaining%20provisions%20of%20these%20Terms%20will%20remain%20in%20effect.%20These%20Terms%20constitute%20the%20entire%20agreement%20between%20us%20regarding%20our%20Service%2C%20and%20supersede%20and%20replace%20any%20prior%20agreements%20we%20might%20have%20between%20us%20regarding%20the%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%0A%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Ch6%3EChanges%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Cp%3EWe%20reserve%20the%20right%2C%20at%20our%20sole%20discretion%2C%20to%20modify%20or%20replace%20these%20Terms%20at%20any%20time.%20If%20a%20revision%20is%20material%20we%20will%20try%20to%20provide%20at%20least%2030%20days%20notice%20prior%20to%20any%20new%20terms%20taking%20effect.%20What%20constitutes%20a%20material%20change%20will%20be%20determined%20at%20our%20sole%20discretion.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Cp%3EBy%20continuing%20to%20access%20or%20use%20our%20Service%20after%20those%20revisions%20become%20effective%2C%20you%20agree%20to%20be%20bound%20by%20the%20revised%20terms.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20agree%20to%20the%20new%20terms%2C%20please%20stop%20using%20the%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Ch6%3EContact%20Us%3C%2Fh6%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20any%20questions%20about%20these%20Terms%2C%20please%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boredbutton.com%2Fcontact%22%3Econtact%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%20via%20Bored%20Button%20LLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%09%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22antihero%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Cdiv%20id%3D%22footer%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22footer-image%22%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3Cp%20class%3D%22footer%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2F%22%3EHome%3C%2Fa%3E%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%7C%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fterms%22%20rel%3D%22nofollow%22%3ETerms%3C%2Fa%3E%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%7C%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%22%2Fprivacy%22%20rel%3D%22nofollow%22%3EPrivacy%3C%2Fa%3E%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%7C%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.totallyuselesswebsite